wannier-minimize nIterations 20000 energyDiffThreshold 1e-11

wannier-center W 1 d+(+5/2)
wannier-center W 1 d+(+3/2)
wannier-center W 1 d+(+1/2)
wannier-center W 1 d+(-1/2)
